because of her sister.

752
01:16:42,227 --> 01:16:45,563
Danielle...
 And the time
we had the picnic.

753
01:16:45,647 --> 01:16:50,443
That's right, the picnic.
And people have come to see us.

754
01:16:50,485 --> 01:16:52,779
To see you, yes.
I remember.

755
01:16:52,821 --> 01:16:56,658
What else do you remember?
She is not just one.

756
01:16:56,700 --> 01:16:59,285
They were all my friends.
They were... They were your friends.

757
01:16:59,369 --> 01:17:01,997
Oh, Dominique, it's okay.
They brought...

758
01:17:02,080 --> 01:17:04,040
Thank you, Charlie.
Their picnic lunches...

759
01:17:04,124 --> 01:17:06,626
