their little children.

761
01:17:08,920 --> 01:17:11,673
Ah, yes. I remember that.
They gave you treats.

762
01:17:11,756 --> 01:17:13,800
Little cakes, candies...
Yes, an apple... You gave me an apple.

763
01:17:13,883 --> 01:17:16,678
Apples, yes.
And then they asked...

764
01:17:16,761 --> 01:17:18,722
