Yes.

765
01:17:18,805 --> 01:17:22,058
Dominique didn't like
the children very much.
Is that right, Dominique?

766
01:17:22,142 --> 01:17:26,938
No, she said that
they were laughing at us.
Do you remember?

767
01:17:27,022 --> 01:17:29,733
No, I can't remember.
Go back. Try.

768
01:17:29,816 --> 01:17:33,069
What did they call you?
I-I can't remember that.

769
01:17:33,153 --> 01:17:35,405
Try to remember what they called you.
Go away, please!

770
01:17:35,488 --> 01:17:38,199
You can remember.
"You" can "remember. Look at me."
I can't remember. No!

771
01:17:38,241 --> 01:17:41,369
Look at me!
Go away! I can't remember that.

772
01:17:41,453 --> 01:17:44,998
"You" can "remember."
What did they call you?
No. I don't know!

773
01:17:45,081 --> 01:17:48,418
Remember!
