"Look at the freak."

774
01:17:48,501 --> 01:17:51,713
... the freak, the freak...
Sweetie, smile.

775
01:17:51,755 --> 01:17:54,424
... the freak, the freak...
 Smile.

776
01:17:54,507 --> 01:17:58,053
 Make them go away
from me, please.

777
01:17:58,136 --> 01:18:00,221
Don't you remember what you learned
last spring that you could never have?

778
01:18:00,305 --> 01:18:03,224
No, I can't remember.
No, I can't remember!
Yes, you can. Try.

779
01:18:03,308 --> 01:18:05,602
Don't you remember you realized
you could have no home,

780
01:18:05,685 --> 01:18:08,688
