Yes, I remember that.

781
01:18:09,689 --> 01:18:11,566
Yes, I remember that.

782
01:18:21,493 --> 01:18:24,871
You're supposed
to be sleeping.

783
01:18:29,668 --> 01:18:35,090
Why can't you
make her go away?

784
01:18:35,173 --> 01:18:39,969
Can you make her go away?
Please. Please.

785
01:18:42,931 --> 01:18:45,141
Of course.

786
01:19:00,740 --> 01:19:05,036
Help me.
Don't let him hurt me.

787
01:19:05,120 --> 01:19:09,165
Help me.
Help me.

788
01:19:54,502 --> 01:19:57,714
 Danielle,
what happened afterward?

789
01:19:57,797 --> 01:20:01,301
L... I was walking in the garden...

790
01:20:01,343 --> 01:20:03,428
with Dominique and...

791
01:20:03,511 --> 01:20:08,099
I tried to tell her that
I was going to have a baby.

792
01:20:08,183 --> 01:20:11,102
And l...

793
01:20:13,021 --> 01:20:16,775
I tried to explain that
it could be her baby too, but...

794
01:20:16,858 --> 01:20:21,905
but she doesn't understand
and she get very angry at me.

795
01:20:21,988 --> 01:20:26,868
And she... tried to kill
the baby with the garden shear.

796
01:20:26,951 --> 01:20:29,579
Are you in pain?

797
01:20:29,663 --> 01:20:32,666
I'm-I'm going
to lose my baby.

798
01:20:32,707 --> 01:20:35,460
No,
you will be fine.

799
01:20:35,543 --> 01:20:39,422
I'm going to die.
Everything will be fine.

800
01:20:39,506 --> 01:20:45,345
Everything will be fine.
Everything will be fine.

801
01:20:45,387 --> 01:20:47,389
Oh, it hurts me.
Please help me.

802
01:20:47,472 --> 01:20:51,184
 Do not be afraid.
Do not be afraid.

803
01:20:51,226 --> 01:20:53,186
Do not be afraid.

804
01:20:53,228 --> 01:20:57,899
I am a surgeon.
You have lost our baby.

805
01:20:57,982 --> 01:21:01,277
You are
bleeding very badly.

806
01:21:01,361 --> 01:21:06,616
The only way I can save you
is to separate you from Dominique.

807
01:21:06,700 --> 01:21:08,994
 Am I going to die?
 No.

808
01:21:09,077 --> 01:21:13,456
You will be fine.
Everything will be fine.

809
01:21:13,540 --> 01:21:19,421
Sleep.
Sleep. Sleep.

810
01:22:24,694 --> 01:22:27,322
Relax, relax,
relax, relax.

811
01:22:29,824 --> 01:22:35,288
Relax. Sleep. Sleep. Sleep.

812
01:22:36,873 --> 01:22:38,833
I-I am sure you've
come back, Dominique.

813
01:22:38,917 --> 01:22:40,877
Dominique! Dominique.
Dominique is dead.

814
01:22:40,960 --> 01:22:43,463
Please come back,
Dominique.

815
01:22:43,505 --> 01:22:46,633
Dominique is dead.
Remember.

816
01:22:46,716 --> 01:22:48,510
No, she's not dead.
She's going to kill you.

817
01:22:48,551 --> 01:22:50,136
She "is" dead.
No!

818
01:22:50,220 --> 01:22:53,515
I know she's not. No! No, she's not.
Sleep.

819
01:22:53,598 --> 01:22:57,977
Sleep. Sleep. Sleep. Sleep.
No. No...

820
01:22:58,019 --> 01:23:02,899
She's not.
Dominique is dead. She is dead.

821
01:23:02,982 --> 01:23:06,361
Time you learn
to accept her death.

822
01:23:08,988 --> 01:23:11,616
We both have
to go away now.

823
01:23:11,700 --> 01:23:15,412
Danielle, I'm going
to marry you.

824
01:23:15,495 --> 01:23:20,583
Do you remember?
How we came here to the clinic...

825
01:23:20,667 --> 01:23:24,004
and made it our own?

826
01:23:24,045 --> 01:23:29,050
It was good
for a while.

827
01:23:29,134 --> 01:23:33,513
But Dominique
