828
01:23:33,555 --> 01:23:37,517
You kept her alive
in your mind.

829
01:23:38,768 --> 01:23:43,356
Sometimes... Sometimes,
you even became her...

830
01:23:43,398 --> 01:23:47,986
to reassure yourself
of her existence.

831
01:23:48,069 --> 01:23:51,990
You could never
accept the guilt,

832
01:23:52,073 --> 01:23:57,537
The terrible guilt
for Dominique's death.

833
01:23:57,620 --> 01:24:01,958
It was hard for me
to accept what had happened...

834
01:24:02,042 --> 01:24:07,005
