together as man and wife.

835
01:24:07,088 --> 01:24:10,342
Every time
I made love to you,

836
01:24:10,425 --> 01:24:13,053
Dominique came back...

837
01:24:13,094 --> 01:24:16,723
and took control of you.

838
01:24:16,806 --> 01:24:20,852
