843
01:24:33,948 --> 01:24:38,370
Dominique is dangerous
for both of us.

844
01:24:38,453 --> 01:24:40,372
To Dominique,

845
01:24:40,455 --> 01:24:45,585
any man that made love
to you is me...

846
01:24:45,627 --> 01:24:48,421
Emil.

847
01:24:48,463 --> 01:24:54,344
 Danielle? Danielle?
I love you.

