850
01:25:30,046 --> 01:25:34,134
Remember. Remember.

851
01:25:36,094 --> 01:25:40,807
Remember. That's it.

852
01:25:45,520 --> 01:25:49,024
What happened?
There was a cake.

853
01:25:49,107 --> 01:25:52,152
A cake?
What else?

854
01:25:52,193 --> 01:25:54,946
They had candles.

855
01:25:55,030 --> 01:25:58,158
Yes.
What did you do?

856
01:25:58,241 --> 01:26:00,910
I made a wish,
Yes.

857
01:26:00,994 --> 01:26:04,706
And I blew out the candles.
Yes.

858
01:26:04,748 --> 01:26:07,208
And then I cut him!

859
01:28:06,619 --> 01:28:09,122
Relax, fellas.
He's dead.

860
01:28:16,004 --> 01:28:18,340
Just a minute,
Mrs. Breton.

861
01:28:18,423 --> 01:28:21,718
Are you prepared to confess to the
murder of your husband, Emil Breton?

862
01:28:21,801 --> 01:28:26,056
I warn you that whatever you say
may be used as evidence against you.

863
01:28:28,767 --> 01:28:31,519
