866
01:28:45,575 --> 01:28:47,535
Dawson.

867
01:29:34,082 --> 01:29:39,129
Well, Miss Collier, up and about?

868
01:29:39,212 --> 01:29:42,507
How do you feel today?
Oh, fine. Thanks.

869
01:29:42,590 --> 01:29:45,218
Oh, thank you for the chocolates.
Oh, you're welcome.

870
01:29:45,260 --> 01:29:47,637
Would you like one?
No, thank you.

871
01:29:47,721 --> 01:29:52,058
Well, you'll be interested to know
